flowchart TD
    SIGNAL([Valid Entry Signal]) --> G1{Consecutive losses\n< max? V10.13}
    G1 -->|No| BLOCK1([Blocked:\nConsec Loss Stop])
    G1 -->|Yes| G2{Direction losses\n< 3 today?}
    G2 -->|No| BLOCK2([Blocked:\nCircuit Breaker])
    G2 -->|Yes| G3{BOS entry?}
    G3 -->|Yes| G4{BOS daily loss\nlimit reached?}
    G3 -->|No| G5
    G4 -->|Yes| BLOCK3([Blocked:\nBOS Loss Limit])
    G4 -->|No| G5{Open trades\n< 3?}
    G5 -->|No| BLOCK4([Blocked:\nMax Open Trades])
    G5 -->|Yes| SIZING[Position Sizing]

    SIZING --> S1{How many trades\ncurrently open?}
    S1 -->|0 open| CT3[3 Contracts\nT1 + T2 + Runner]
    S1 -->|1+ open| CT2[2 Contracts\nT1 + T2, no Runner]

    CT3 --> RETRACE{Retrace entry?\nRisk > 8 pts?\nES/MES only}
    CT2 --> RETRACE
    RETRACE -->|Yes| CT1[Force: 1 Contract\nV10.11 Risk Cap]
    RETRACE -->|No| ENTER([Open Trade])
    CT1 --> ENTER
